{"article_id":"GjntzqHJ1nUlns3d","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"President Trump on Saturday criticized Puerto Rico 's `` poor leadership ''","depth":5},{"id":1,"text":"and defended his administration 's response to the aftermath of Hurricane Maria in an early morning series of tweets","depth":6},{"id":2,"text":"that earned immediate backlash from Democrats and other critics .","depth":6},{"id":3,"text":"Following a plea for aid on Friday by San Juan 's mayor ,","depth":7},{"id":4,"text":"Trump said","depth":8},{"id":5,"text":"the mayor was being `` nasty . ''","depth":8},{"id":6,"text":"\" The mayor of San Juan ,","depth":9},{"id":7,"text":"who was very complimentary only a few days ago ,","depth":9},{"id":8,"text":"has now been told by the Democrats","depth":9},{"id":9,"text":"that you must be nasty to Trump , \"","depth":9},{"id":10,"text":"Trump tweeted .","depth":7},{"id":11,"text":"`` Such poor leadership ability by the mayor of San Juan , and others in Puerto Rico ,","depth":7},{"id":12,"text":"who are not able to get their workers to help . ''","depth":7},{"id":13,"text":"`` They want everything to be done for them","depth":9},{"id":14,"text":"when it should be a community effort , ''","depth":9},{"id":15,"text":"he continued .","depth":8},{"id":16,"text":"`` 10,000 Federal workers now on Island","depth":8},{"id":17,"text":"doing a fantastic job . ''","depth":8},{"id":18,"text":"San Juan Mayor Carmen Yulín Cruz held an emotional press conference Friday","depth":6},{"id":19,"text":"ripping the Trump administration ' s efforts","depth":7},{"id":20,"text":"to assist the island .","depth":7},{"id":21,"text":"`` I will do what I never thought","depth":8},{"id":22,"text":"I was going to do .","depth":8},{"id":23,"text":"I am begging ,","depth":9},{"id":24,"text":"begging anyone","depth":11},{"id":25,"text":"who can hear us","depth":11},{"id":26,"text":"to save us from dying .","depth":10},{"id":27,"text":"If anybody out there is listening to us ,","depth":9},{"id":28,"text":"we are dying ,","depth":10},{"id":29,"text":"and you are killing us with the inefficiency , ''","depth":10},{"id":30,"text":"she said .","depth":6},{"id":31,"text":"On Saturday ,","depth":7},{"id":32,"text":"following Trump 's tweets about her ,","depth":8},{"id":33,"text":"Cruz said","depth":8},{"id":34,"text":"her top goal is `` saving lives . ''","depth":6},{"id":35,"text":"`` Actually , I was asking for help .","depth":8},{"id":36,"text":"I was n't saying anything nasty about the president , ''","depth":8},{"id":37,"text":"Cruz said on MSNBC","depth":8},{"id":38,"text":"following the tweets .","depth":8},{"id":39,"text":"`` It 's not about politics ,","depth":8},{"id":40,"text":"it 's not about petty comments ,","depth":8},{"id":41,"text":"it 's about moving forward ,","depth":8},{"id":42,"text":"putting boots on the ground","depth":9},{"id":43,"text":"and saving lives . \"","depth":9},{"id":44,"text":"Democrats slammed Trump 's response to Cruz and his relief efforts for the U.S. territory .","depth":5},{"id":45,"text":"\" Is your ego so fragile","depth":8},{"id":46,"text":"& your heart so cold","depth":8},{"id":47,"text":"that you ' d attack a leader in the midst of a humanitarian crisis","depth":8},{"id":48,"text":"because she needs your help ? \"","depth":8},{"id":49,"text":"Rep. Bonnie Watson Coleman","depth":8},{"id":50,"text":"( D-N.J. )","depth":8},{"id":51,"text":"tweeted at Trump on Saturday .","depth":7},{"id":52,"text":"\" You watch TV","depth":6},{"id":53,"text":"& tweet insults at their leaders from your golf club , \"","depth":6},{"id":54,"text":"Rep. Don Beyer","depth":7},{"id":55,"text":"( D-Va. )","depth":7},{"id":56,"text":"tweeted .","depth":6},{"id":57,"text":"The Mayor of San Juan ,","depth":9},{"id":58,"text":"who was very complimentary only a few days ago ,","depth":9},{"id":59,"text":"has now been told by the Democrats","depth":8},{"id":60,"text":"that you must be nasty to Trump .","depth":7},{"id":61,"text":"- Donald J. Trump","depth":8},{"id":62,"text":"( @ realDonaldTrump )","depth":8},{"id":63,"text":"September 30 , 2017 ...","depth":7},{"id":64,"text":"Such poor leadership ability by the Mayor of San Juan , and others in Puerto Rico ,","depth":8},{"id":65,"text":"who are not able to get their workers to help .","depth":8},{"id":66,"text":"They ....","depth":7},{"id":67,"text":"- Donald J. Trump","depth":9},{"id":68,"text":"( @ realDonaldTrump )","depth":9},{"id":69,"text":"September 30 , 2017 ... want everything to be done for them","depth":8},{"id":70,"text":"when it should be a community effort .","depth":7},{"id":71,"text":"10,000 Federal workers now on Island","depth":7},{"id":72,"text":"doing a fantastic job .","depth":7},{"id":73,"text":"- Donald J. Trump","depth":8},{"id":74,"text":"( @ realDonaldTrump )","depth":8},{"id":75,"text":"September 30 , 2017","depth":7},{"id":76,"text":"The military and first responders ,","depth":8},{"id":77,"text":"despite no electric , roads , phones etc. ,","depth":8},{"id":78,"text":"have done an amazing job .","depth":7},{"id":79,"text":"Puerto Rico was totally destroyed .","depth":7},{"id":80,"text":"- Donald J. Trump","depth":9},{"id":81,"text":"( @ realDonaldTrump )","depth":9},{"id":82,"text":"September 30 , 2017","depth":8},{"id":83,"text":"Cruz ,","depth":5},{"id":84,"text":"who is a member of the island 's Popular Democratic Party ,","depth":5},{"id":85,"text":"is just one element of the active pressure on the Trump administration over what critics are saying is a slow response to the hurricane devastation .","depth":4},{"id":86,"text":"Numerous officials in Puerto Rico are warning","depth":6},{"id":87,"text":"it could be a humanitarian disaster .","depth":6},{"id":88,"text":"The island has been without water or power","depth":7},{"id":89,"text":"since Hurricane Maria hit a week ago .","depth":7},{"id":90,"text":"The Federal Emergency Management Agency sent airplanes and ships with food , water and generators","depth":8},{"id":91,"text":"and 10,000 federal employees have been deployed","depth":9},{"id":92,"text":"to help in both Puerto Rico and the U.S. Virgin Islands ,","depth":10},{"id":93,"text":"which was also hit .","depth":10},{"id":94,"text":"The three-star general","depth":10},{"id":95,"text":"recently put in charge of U.S. military relief operations in Puerto Rico","depth":10},{"id":96,"text":"said Friday","depth":9},{"id":97,"text":"that there are as many as 4,600 troops on the ground in Puerto Rico","depth":10},{"id":98,"text":"- including members of the National Guard and Reserves -","depth":10},{"id":99,"text":"and the Pentagon would be sending more troops and vehicles to the island ,","depth":10},{"id":100,"text":"where residents could be without power for six months .","depth":10},{"id":101,"text":"Trump also temporarily lifted the Jones Act ,","depth":5},{"id":102,"text":"which requires American-made and -operated vessels to transport cargo between U.S. ports ,","depth":7},{"id":103,"text":"including Puerto Rico ,","depth":7},{"id":104,"text":"in order to bolster relief by ship to the island .","depth":6},{"id":105,"text":"Trump has not acknowledged anything lacking in his administration ' s response to the crisis","depth":4},{"id":106,"text":"but this week blamed the media","depth":6},{"id":107,"text":"for allegedly trying to \" get Trump \"","depth":7},{"id":108,"text":"by disparaging aide workers .","depth":7},{"id":109,"text":"He also blamed the distance between the island and the mainland U.S.","depth":6},{"id":110,"text":"for hampering relief .","depth":6},{"id":111,"text":"Trump insisted Friday","depth":7},{"id":112,"text":"that his administration is doing an \" incredible job \" with relief efforts .","depth":7},{"id":113,"text":"`` We have done an incredible job ,","depth":8},{"id":114,"text":"considering there 's absolutely nothing","depth":10},{"id":115,"text":"to work with , ''","depth":10},{"id":116,"text":"Trump told reporters at the White House .","depth":9},{"id":117,"text":"`` And a very big question is , what are we going to do with the power plant ?","depth":10},{"id":118,"text":"Because the power plant is totally wiped out , ''","depth":10},{"id":119,"text":"he said .","depth":9},{"id":120,"text":"`` There is nothing .","depth":9},{"id":121,"text":"The power grid is gone . ''","depth":9},{"id":122,"text":"He also said on Friday","depth":7},{"id":123,"text":"that Puerto Ricans are `` unable to get involved '' in relief efforts .","depth":7},{"id":124,"text":"\" They 're taking care of their families","depth":9},{"id":125,"text":"and largely unable to get involved ,","depth":10},{"id":126,"text":"largely unable to help , \"","depth":10},{"id":127,"text":"he said .","depth":8},{"id":128,"text":"\" Therefore , we 're forced to bring in truck drivers , security and many , many other personnel by the thousands .","depth":9},{"id":129,"text":"And we 're bringing them onto the island","depth":10},{"id":130,"text":"as we speak .","depth":10},{"id":131,"text":"We 've never seen a situation like this . \"","depth":8},{"id":132,"text":"However , Cruz has taken the media spotlight","depth":7},{"id":133,"text":"to warn","depth":8},{"id":134,"text":"that not enough is being done","depth":9},{"id":135,"text":"to help her city and the island .","depth":9},{"id":136,"text":"In an interview with CNN ' s Anderson Cooper Friday night , Cruz wore a shirt","depth":8},{"id":137,"text":"emblazoned with the words","depth":9},{"id":138,"text":"\" help us ,","depth":10},{"id":139,"text":"we are dying . \"","depth":10},{"id":140,"text":"Alicia Cohn , Melanie Zanona and Mike Lillis contributed .","depth":7},{"id":141,"text":"Updated 10:45 a.m .","depth":5}],"relations":[{"parent":283,"left":224,"right":282,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":224,"left":185,"right":223,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":185,"left":159,"right":184,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":159,"left":144,"right":158,"relation":"e